thread.title: WITHDRAWN: Community mourns as FBI backlash grows.

title: WITHDRAWN: Community mourns as FBI backlash grows.
text:
WITHDRAWN: Community mourns as FBI backlash grows. Saturday, February 17, 2018 - 00:30 
As more funerals get underway for victims of the Florida school massacre, the pressure is mounting for FBI director Christopher Wray to resign after his agency admitted it failed to investigate a warning on the accused gunman. Jillian Kitchener reports.
